<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246625>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56 – 59. Biology of Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti. 56, host plant Helianthemum nummularium. 57, mine, adaxial view. 58, excrements of larva in mine, adaxial view. 59, transparent cocoon outside the mine. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246625/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246626>
    dc:description "FIGURES 60 – 61. Diagnostic characters in Triberta head vestiture of adults. 60, vertex of the neotype of Lithocolletis cistifoliella Groschke, 1944. 61, vertex of the lectotype of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246626/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246620>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 25. Female genitalia of Triberta species. 22, Triberta cistifoliella, Greece, prep. TRB 3559 ♀. Scale bar 200 µm. 23, same preparation, signum on corpus bursae, prep. TRB 3559 ♀. Scale bar 100 µm. 24, Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti, prep. DP 3807 ♀. Scale bar 200 µm. 25, same preparation, signum on corpus bursae, prep. DP 3807 ♀. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246618>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 15. The primary types of Triberta species. 10, the neotype of Lithocolletis cistifoliella Groschke, 1944, male, in ZSM. 11, the lectotype of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, in ZMHB. 12, the paralectotype 1 of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, in ZMHB. 13, the paralectotype 2 of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, in ZMHB. 14, the paralectotype 3 of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, female, in ZMHB. 15, the paralectotype 4 of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, female, in ZMHB. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246619>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 21. Male genitalia of Triberta species. 16, Lithocolletis cistifoliella Groschke, 1944, male, neotype, prep. TRB 3554 ♂, in ZSM. 17, Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, lectotype, prep. TRB 3935 ♂, in ZMHB. 18, Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, paralectotype, prep. TRB 3945 ♂, in ZMHB. 19, Valva of Triberta helianthemella, male, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti, prep. TRB 3552 ♂, in MSNV. Scale bar 100 µm. 20, abdomen opening of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, lectotype, prep. TRB 3935 ♂, in ZMHB. Scale bar 200 µm. 21, sternum VIII of Lithocolletis helianthemella Herrich-Schäffer, 1861, male, lectotype, prep. TRB 3935 ♂, in ZMHB. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246619/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246621>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 31. Head of late instar larva of Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti. 26, frontal view. 27, lateral view. 28, mouthparts. 29, mandibles and hypopharynx, ventral view. 30, ventral surface of head. 31, maxillary palpus. Scale bar as indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246622>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38 – 43. Prolegs of Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti. 38, ventral view. 39, crochets in rest position, ventral view. 40, crochets in open position, ventral view. 41, caudal segments. 42, abdominal segment A 9, dorsal view. 43, caudal prolegs, ventral view. Scale bar as indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246623>
    dc:description "FIGURES 44 – 49. Pupa of Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti. 44, ventral view. 45, lateral view. 46, pupal head. 47, A pair of frontal sensillae on pupal head. 48, sclerotized ridge on pupal segments A 2. 49, sclerotized ridge on pupal segments A 6 - 8. Scale bar as indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246623/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246624>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 – 55. P upa of Triberta helianthemella, Italy, Verona, 25 / 30. vi. 2010, leg. P. Triberti. 50, dorsal surface of segment A 1. 51, dorsal surface of segment A 8. 52, segments A 8 - 9, lateral view. 53, caudal segment, dorsal view. 54, A 10, caudal view. 55, nodule on caudal protuberance. Scale bar as indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246624/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

